{
  "stem": "9987.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some people, I don't know what they did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had no choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We made a choice-- the family made a choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we are going to come to the registration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It came Monday morning, at 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody took a little bundle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father, my mother, my sister Berta with her two children, her husband Jakobowitz, the four brothers, and some cousins of ours, we came out to the marketplace, and we're standing-- and ready for that registration.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The door was left open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we're standing and waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "By approximately 9 o'clock, all of a sudden, trucks coming in, the Ukraine police, Polish police, German police, SS, they encircled the whole marketplace.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We are standing in the middle, approximately 2,000 to 3,000 people, old, young, middle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We are standing and waiting and don't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they started the selection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They started to pick up all the old people, approximately 400 to 500 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Put them in one side.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The rest are still standing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Among these old people was my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Trucks pulled up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They loaded them in the trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Whoever couldn't get on, they threw him on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in the last truck, soldiers with-- with machine guns, and they drove away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We didn't know where, what, where, and when-- but it took approximately an hour and a half.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were back, empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We found out later that there-- there was a mass grave prepared about 10 kilometers away, up in-- in the forest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The name of the place is Dukla.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They all were shot over there, and put into a mass grave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's where I suspect my father is, still.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
